title: Naruto part 1 (vol 1-27, 244 chapters)
description:
The popular manga series Naruto by Kishimoto Masashi is divided into two parts - this is the first one!

The first part of the series contains the first 27 volumes (244 chapter, incl. Kakashi Gaiden). Download, seed, read, seed, and enjoy! ;)
